name: Tour du monde
body:
Simple cartographic application, which began as a demo-project for the [Carousel library](https://github.com/yudjin87/carousel), and then evolved to the self-contained application. This app has to help me to travel around the World in ~80 Days!

![](https://github.com/yudjin87/tour_du_monde/blob/gh-pages/imgs/tour_de_monde.png?raw=true)
